{"id":"b50436fb-ef29-407d-beec-313bd371ae5d","title":"1550/08/07: To Lionardo di Buonarroto Simoni","type":"main-list-block","children":[{"id":"52ea2d91-ca7e-4529-90ce-4685d1d28390","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"From Rome, August 7th, 1550.","standoffProperties":[{"id":"c6ab6da0-991c-4b0a-947b-6fc64228c476","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":5,"end":8,"value":"501a8a32-2c8a-4934-9060-8c7e36339f0f","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"9613be2c-eb5f-4b3c-8ea2-99f28fdb5a4b","type":"codex/time-reference","start":11,"end":26,"value":"c0194936-d540-40e7-8f6e-261fb0ad4e9f","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"de0df47c-d190-4f24-89c9-c07e694edcfd","type":"style/superscript","start":19,"end":20,"value":null,"zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]}],"blockProperties":[]},{"id":"c52d114a-d7f1-4231-b8ba-b43b47677f8d","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"To Lionardo di Buonarroto Simoni,","standoffProperties":[{"id":"05307c4c-e568-4144-9d10-55a989b6c419","type":"style/italics","start":0,"end":31,"value":null,"zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"fba5558e-4e9e-4496-9f5f-a7ce40e9d58a","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":3,"end":31,"value":"93ce2119-f2b8-4642-b551-7b8ca6b1ed96","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]}],"blockProperties":[]},{"id":"01909ea7-fe04-40bf-ae1b-f5bfc4a3e5f0","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"in Florence.","standoffProperties":[{"id":"aad8ae4b-c7e5-4256-977e-6008cda692ec","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":3,"end":10,"value":"671ee7e7-ae1b-4a5a-9591-b40203d5108f","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]}],"blockProperties":[]},{"id":"4f71cb4c-7311-43f1-b8c3-749ddb035e2b","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"","standoffProperties":[],"blockProperties":[]},{"id":"7f1ca9ed-c00f-4872-a277-335af24cc1b5","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"Lionardo,\u00A0\u2014\u00A0After the arrival of the Trebbiano and the shirts I had no further occasion to write to thee, but it would now be advisable for me to have in my possession the two Briefs drawn up by Pope Paul referring to the provision granted to me for life by His Holiness while I was in his service in Rome.\u00A0These Briefs were sent to thee among the other documents in that box thou hast received and would have leaden seals attached to them. Thou wilt easily recognise which they are. They can be wrapped up in a piece of waxed cloth and put into a small box securely done up. If thou canst arrange to send them to me by a trustworthy person who will be sure to take care of them, send them on and make the carrier give thee such security against their loss as in thy judgment will assure their safe delivery. I wish to show them to the Pope [Julius III.] so that he may understand that according to them I am His Holiness\u0027 creditor for, I think, more than two thousand crowns\u00A0\u2014\u00A0not that it is likely to be of any\u00A0use to me, but merely for my own satisfaction. I think the letter-carrier might be able to bring them\u00A0as it would be only a small packet.","standoffProperties":[{"id":"dc100fc4-477c-457b-b1cd-d05b74fe0a58","type":"style/uppercase","start":0,"end":7,"value":null,"zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"2de29715-8b73-49b8-b60a-3c19e56c0368","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":0,"end":7,"value":"93ce2119-f2b8-4642-b551-7b8ca6b1ed96","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"10f479c5-55b6-41e4-beea-b8e8ea7342a9","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":37,"end":45,"value":"60646193-58d9-4d5a-82a1-fc7fdb88be23","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"f49a3899-50ae-4fc5-baa7-0660c5b4874a","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":62,"end":62,"value":"add92e01-cefe-4f13-94dd-f00eb82155b0","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"ae9c63f0-97b9-4bfe-9afa-dac0292c1b77","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":100,"end":103,"value":"93ce2119-f2b8-4642-b551-7b8ca6b1ed96","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"7fc6c8a7-ec69-47c1-9825-a5bafea048f8","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":140,"end":141,"value":"add92e01-cefe-4f13-94dd-f00eb82155